title: Hearts_Rajneeshpuram.mp4
description:
Documentary about an unique commune , Rajneeshpuram, Oregon, US
1981-1985
In 5 years it was created in a desert, place,like paradise, of joy, laughter, enthusiasm for living in new way. Simple houses for 5000 people were all air-conditioned. Commune was self-sufficient. It was destroyed by US government and by power-game of person (little group) who was practically leading commune while Osho was in silence
